{"tid":910677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"央視女記者大鬧英國座談會 檢方認定罪證不足不起訴","createTime":"2018-11-21T10:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T13:38:35.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5b4d957a8351d57acc9ab6099a82759ef7ba5241","tid":910677,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phprwcKZ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phprwcKZ6.jpg&h=3edcb685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國央視記者孔琳琳先前在一場於英國舉辦的座談會上失控叫罵，甚至還掌摑一名學生，事後遭控普通襲擊。如今檢方以罪證不足為由，撤銷對孔琳琳的控訴。<br />\n<br />\n根據《衛報》報導，「英格蘭及威爾斯皇家檢察署」（CPS）發言人說明，檢方在檢視現有證據後，認定孔琳琳普通襲擊一案罪證不足，遂決定撤銷控訴。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生在一場於英國伯明罕舉辦的「香港自由、法治、自治受損」座談會，會中孔琳琳情緒失控，大罵在場的香港監察主席羅傑斯（Benedict Rogers）是騙子，意圖分裂中國，還連續打了香港留學生志工兩巴掌，事後遭控告普通襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n此案在當時衍生為外交風波，中國大使館抨擊英國保守黨干涉中國內政，認為該名女記者被剝奪發表意見、觀點的權利，要求活動主辦方道歉。主辦方及羅傑斯駁斥中方說法，指現場80多人親眼看到孔女打人，認為她才應該道歉，中方也應收回聲明。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2619678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2619678&d=WFg%2BS0Xu3VzYSHNt7AiMI8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=8627658a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2619678&h=016b1944\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2619678</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da89132fa21c52cdf7a14fa37f2552a709d0e95","tid":910677,"uid":117856,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇拍到片